   "question": "Where does Holy Paladin Phase 4 BiS come from?",
   "answer": "From the gear worn by 339 top-ranked Holy Paladin healing parses on Warcraft Logs during Phase 4 (Zul'Aman), aggregated per slot — what high parsers actually equip, not a spreadsheet ideal."
