  {
   "question": "What are the highest-consensus Holy Paladin items in Phase 4?",
   "answer": "Lightbringer Chestpiece (87%), Lightbringer Leggings (82%), Lightbringer Pauldrons (75%). When an item sits above ~70% among top parsers, treat it as the priority drop to chase."
  },
  {
   "question": "Should I follow this list exactly for Phase 4?",
